      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it feels like a joke, you know? like i'm just sitting here waiting for the floor to fall out. everyone thinks i have it all figured out but i'm just... i'm just a fraud. even if i tried to start over, the debt alone makes it impossible. there's no way back from this. i'm just tired of pretending there is.",
